{
  "text": "2.6. Western Blotting Analysis. The protein concentrations were analyzed by BCA protein assay kit (P0012, Beyotime, China). Protein levels of mTOR, p-mTOR, and GCLc were detected by western blotting assay with an mTOR antibody (sc-1549, Santa Cruz Biotech), a p-mTOR antibody (S2448) [CITATION_1] Oxidative Medicine and Cellular Longevity (sc-101738, Santa Cruz Biotech), and a GCLc antibody (BA1627, BOSTER), respectively. Each experiment was repeated at least three times.",
